Chart configuration (Chart.js)

Use a mixed chart (type: 'bar' at the dataset level, with type: 'line' for the potential series; for Intraday use type: 'line' with fill: true on all three).

Colors (use getComputedStyle to read CSS vars, OR hardcode HSL strings):

    Solar (toGrid): hsl(45, 95%, 55%)
    BESS (toBESS): hsl(200, 70%, 50%)
    Potential (dashed): hsl(215, 12%, 35%)
    NOW reference line: hsl(0, 72%, 55%)
    Grid lines: hsl(220, 15%, 18%)
    Tick text: hsl(215, 12%, 35%), fontSize 10
    Tooltip bg: hsl(220, 18%, 13%), border hsl(220, 15%, 20%)

